# ============================================
# IMPORTANT NOTES
# ============================================

# 1. EMBEDDING_DIMENSION must match your chosen model:
#    - keepitreal/vietnamese-sbert → 384
#    - hiieu/halong_embedding → 768
#    - bkai-foundation-models/vietnamese-embedding-v1 → 768
#    - all-MiniLM-L6-v2 → 384

# 2. If you change EMBEDDING_DIMENSION, you MUST:
#    - Drop and recreate the embeddings table
#    - Rebuild all embeddings
#    - See VECTOR_DIMENSION_FIX.md for detailed instructions

# 3. To fix dimension mismatch errors:
#    - Run: python scripts/check_vector_dimension.py (diagnose)
#    - Run: python scripts/fix_vector_dimension.py (fix)
#    - Rebuild: python scripts/build_embeddings.py

